                    <msContents class="lemmatic">
                        <summary>
                            The manuscript contains the following works:
                            1) Introduction of Abd Latif Baghdadi's commentary on the Aphorisims in <locus>ff. 1-2, 247</locus>
                            2) a part of IAS's commentary on the Aphorisms in <locus>ff. 3-31</locus>
                            3) Hunayn's Question on Medicine with IAS's commentary in <locus>ff. 31-246.</locus>
                            Item 1 is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on <locus from="1b">f. 1b</locus>; the beginning of each Book is as follows:
                           
                        </summary>
